<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Terms of Service | The Learning Sphere</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --text: #111111;
      --muted: #666666;
      --accent: #000000;
      --border: #e0e0e0;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 16px;
      background-color: black;
    }

    .wrapper {
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 40px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .date {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-top: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
      padding-left: 10px;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    ul {
      margin-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    ul li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    a:hover {
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 60px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="date">Effective Date: <strong>{{effectiveDate}}</strong></p>

    <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p>By accessing or using The Learning Sphere, you agree to these Terms. Please discontinue use if you do not accept these terms.</p>

    <h2>2. Eligibility</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>You must be 13 years or older.</li>
      <li>You agree to provide accurate account details.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Our Mission</h2>
    <p>The Learning Sphere is designed to help students acquire skills with 100% guaranteed learning outcomes via adaptive courses and peer-led teaching.</p>

    <h2>4. Account Responsibility</h2>
    <p>Keep your credentials secure. You are liable for activities under your account. Notify us if you suspect unauthorized access.</p>

    <h2>5. Prohibited Conduct</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>No posting of harmful or unlawful content.</li>
      <li>No platform abuse or security exploitation.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Payments & Refund Policy</h2>
    <p>All payments are final. Refunds are handled per our internal refund policy. Our “Guaranteed Skill Learning” refers to outcome-driven learning, not refund assurance.</p>

    <h2>7. Content & Peer Teachers</h2>
    <p>All content is educational. Peer teachers are verified learners—not certified professionals. Content is provided “as-is.”</p>

    <h2>8. Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>All materials belong to The Learning Sphere or its contributors. Do not redistribute without permission.</p>

    <h2>9. Account Termination</h2>
    <p>We may terminate your account for rule violations or suspicious activity. Misuse may result in legal action.</p>

    <h2>10. Modifications</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to update these Terms. Continued use means you accept changes.</p>

    <h2>11. Liability</h2>
    <p>We are not responsible for indirect damages. The platform is provided as a learning tool, not a guaranteed employment opportunity.</p>

    <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For questions or help, email us at <a href="mailto:support@learningsphere.com">support@learningsphere.com</a></p>

    <footer>
      &copy; {{year}} The Learning Sphere. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
